item.title: CVE-2021-24760|2024-08-03T19:42:16.874Z -- unknown -- gutenberg%20pdf%20viewer%20block
item.description: The Gutenberg PDF Viewer Block WordPress plugin before 1.0.1 does not sanitise and escape its block, which could allow users with a role as low as Contributor to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
